title: Birdhouse_Tony_Hawk_The_Beginning(2007)
description:
The Beginning Skateboard Film by Birdhouse

More than a decade after the release of The End, Birdhouse comes full circle with The Beginning. Filmed on location at secret spots, hideaways and hubbas the world over, The Beginning features the talents of: Matt Ball, Tony Hawk, Steve Nesser, Brian Sumner, Shaun White, Willy Santos and Jeremy Klein. Nipping at the heels of the pros is one of the Birdhouse Amateur team, including: Derek Burdette, Sean Eaton, Justin "Figgy" Figueroa, Shaun Gregorie, Riley Hawk, Nate LaCoste, Jon Dickson, Randy Ploesser and Jean Postec. Watch as The Beginning ushers in a whole new era of skateboarding.
